## ASSESSMENT PHILOSOPHY

No exams. No multiple choice. Every assessment is a cold-handoff test.

- **Can a stranger use your artifact from the file alone?** (Module 1.2)
- **Does your primed review find categories the unprimed review cannot?** (Module 1.3)
- **Does your multi-instance methodology produce findings no single instance could?** (Module 2.3)
- **Does your system satisfy the rings it claims to satisfy?** (Module 5.2)
- **Does your capstone work when the internet doesn't?** (Module 6.5)

The artifact is the assessment. Build the thing. Cold-handoff is the grade.

